<v Speaker 2>Me gustaría.

00:08:03.940 --> 00:08:09.140
<v Speaker 1>So this is a nice hook to remember wood because it's something that's very common that you will use a lot.

00:08:08.479 --> 00:08:14.479
<v Speaker 1>So what is that little bit you need for wood that you can pluck out of Megustaria?

00:08:14.479 --> 00:08:15.840
<v Speaker 2>The IA ending.

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:16.639
<v Speaker 1>Perfect.

00:08:16.639 --> 00:08:18.880
<v Speaker 1>So I would stay for three days

00:08:20.060 --> 00:08:23.100
<v Speaker 2>Me quedaria por tres días.

00:08:23.100 --> 00:08:23.740
<v Speaker 1>Good.

