<v Speaker 1>I would stay for three days, but I have to work and not from memory but thinking it through.

00:08:56.140 --> 00:08:56.780
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:08:57.180 --> 00:08:57.500
<v Speaker 1>So

00:08:57.860 --> 00:09:00.980
<v Speaker 1>Uh thinking it through again, taking that time to think it through again.

00:09:00.980 --> 00:09:04.980
<v Speaker 1>I would stay is the first bit.

00:09:06.420 --> 00:09:06.900
<v Speaker 1>Good.

